title: Oh Maya! Moore hits winner to lift Lynx over Fever 80-77
text:
> Indiana Oh Maya! Moore hits winner to lift Lynx over Fever 80-77 Indiana Fever head coach Stephanie White walks off the court after Game 3 of the WNBA Finals basketball series against against the Minnesota Lynx, Friday, Oct. 9, 2015, in Indianapolis. The Lynx won 80-77. (AP Photo/AJ Mast) iWitness7 is your chance to join the News Center 7 team! Upload your videos and photos and share with the entire WHIO-TV community!
